name: 2021 10th International Conference on Internet Computing for Science and Engineering（ICICSE 2021）
content: Publication： ICICSE 2021 Conference Proceedings (ISBN: 978-1-4503-8495-7): Submissions to the conference will be peer reviewed and accepted papers of ICICSE 2021 will be published in the International Conference Proceedings Series, which will be archived in the ACM Digital Library and submitted for index by Ei Compendex, Scopus, Thomson Reuters Conference Proceedings Citation Index (ISI Web of Science). Journal Publication: IJSSC - International Journal of Space-Based and Situated Computing （http://www.icicse.org/ijssc-si.html） Special Issue on Towards Ubiquitous Computing based on Smart Internet of Medical Things
